{
  "texts": [
    "Results are shown for the 8-16-32 architecture over three independent runs.",
    "Stable training is observed only for intermediate initialization scales (0.01 ≤ c ≤ 0.06), illustrating the high sensitivity of constrained models to weight initialization.",
    "FIG. 4.4FIG.",
    "(a), (b) Test accuracy heatmaps and (c), (d) confusion matrices for (a), (c) constrained and (b), (d) unconstrained SincHSRNNs on the full ten-digit AudioMNIST dataset.",
    "(a), (b) Test accuracy heatmaps show the mean test accuracies (%) across hidden-unit configurations and sampling rates for the constrained and unconstrained networks, respectively."
  ]
